MALARIA CHEMOPROPYLAXIS IN G-6PD DEFICIENCY (3)
===============================================
G-6-PD [glucose-6-phosphate dehydrogenase] deficiency also
affects prophylaxis choice in that one would not
want to give Maloprim, pyrimethamine/dapsone, to
a G-6-PD deficient subject.
--
Hugh de Glanville
e-mail: bjhc@bcs.org.uk
